16:
A crude iron light bowgun that,
despite its mass-produced
quality, packs quite a punch.
20:
A light bowgun of fine steel,
with improved durability and
power for more demanding hunts.
24:
A lavish light bowgun of rare
steel able to pierce even the
hardest of shells with ease.
27:
This light bowgun's Nergigante
scales constantly regrow,
promising unending pain to foes.
29:
The bolts fired from this Nergigante
light bowgun protrude from prey
like grave markers.
31:
A decadent light bowgun lavished
in rich, lustrous Paolumu hide.
34:
A light bowgun of lush Paolumu
hide so lustrous it appears dew-
dappled. For elegant slaying.
38:
A demonic Bazelgeuse bowgun that
scorches the earth with the vast
explosion each shot yields.
41:
Wrapped in supple Jagras hide,
this light bowgun fits firmly in
the user's grip.
45:
Lavish use of butter-soft Jagras
hide makes this light bowgun
feel like a part of its user.
49:
Residual heat in the Rathalos
parts used in this light bowgun
grants its bolts a searing bite.
52:
A light bowgun made host to a
Rathalos' fury, said to be able
to rend earth and sky apart.
55:
New forging techniques have been
used to infuse this iron light
bowgun with elemental power.
58:
Bold yet delicate tweaks have
upped the power and element of
this elemental light bowgun.
66:
A light bowgun made from easily
obtainable bone. Rough-hewn, but
a sturdy friend to new hunters.
70:
Made from the densest of bones,
this light bowgun adds firepower
with the same ease of use.
74:
A light bowgun of modified bone.
The blinding speed of each shot
can easily penetrate solid rock.
77:
Drawing power from beyond death,
this Vaal Hazak light bowgun serves
only those who embrace oblivion.
79:
The bellowing of this Vaal Hazak
light bowgun heralds the end and
the beginning of all eternity.
81:
A light bowgun wrapped in hide
tempered hard as iron in the
searing breath of an Anjanath.
84:
This Anjanath light bowgun's
bolts burn all who come within
its firing range to cinder.
88:
Fortified with Jyuratodus parts
and caked in mud, this light bowgun
is as primal as it is deadly.
92:
Unrivaled in ferocity, a salvo
of shots from this Jyuratodus
bowgun will aerate anything.
96:
Added Lavasioth parts keep this
light bowgun's barrel at furnace
temperatures.
99:
Adding Barroth parts only made
this light bowgun more stark and
brutish...in a good way.
103:
Imbued with the destructive
might of a Barroth, each shot
carves new scars into the earth.
107:
This bloodthirsty Odogaron light
bowgun shimmers with an uncanny,
maddening light.
110:
The moment after this Odogaron
light bowgun's howl shakes the
earth, its prey erupts in red.
113:
A dragon element light bowgun
hewn from bone, crafted by
dark and forbidden means.
117:
A curious bowgun unlike any the
Guild designed. Still, none can
gainsay its functionality.
120:
A light bowgun forged of Kirin
parts via an ancient, unearthed
design that exceeds modern tech.
124:
A dragon element light bowgun
forged in iron, crafted by
dark and forbidden means.
127:
This Kushala Daora light bowgun
rains a storm of icy bullets fit
to shame the worst winter hail.
130:
A Xeno'jiiva light bowgun, lord
among treasures. Its pitiless
judgment pierces all before it.
132:
The original bone bowgun, ideal
for hunting small prey. A fine
companion for fledgling hunters.
135:
A baleful Bowgun said to
have been crafted in a
dark workshop.
138:
A Kulve Taroth light bowgun with
unknown traits. Its true potential
has yet to be realized.
142:
A Kulve Taroth light bowgun that
utilizes other monster parts for
research purposes.
153:
A Kulve Taroth light bowgun that
possesses new properties due to
clever material utilization.
164:
A Kulve Taroth light bowgun that
fully harnesses the hidden power
of the materials used to create it.
168:
A hidden power seeps from
this Lunastra light bowgun, as
if a soul is trapped inside.
170:
This Lunastra light bowgun was
forged in hellfire. Sometimes
guards its user from fatal blows.
172:
This Lunastra light bowgun
resonates with Nergigante parts
to give a chance for regeneration.
174:
This Lunastra light bowgun
resonates with Xeno'jiiva parts
to help conserve ammo.
177:
A unique light bowgun made from
the gold of Kulve Taroth. Houses
the true might of the goddess within.
184:
Crafted specifically for the Defense
Corps, its high-performance
output is thanks to modern tech.
202:
Using only the rarest of metals,
this light bowgun can puncture
even the toughest defense.
206:
This light bowgun is so powerful,
it's almost as if the spirit of a
Yian Garuga possesses it.
209:
Confess thy sins unto me. 
This Ruiner Nergigante light
bowgun perforates the guilty.
212:
A Nightshade Paolumu light
bowgun. The beautiful black fur
glistens with the blood of its foes.
215:
This Glavenus light bowgun
stokes the flame of a hunter's
passion to sear all before them.
217:
Shots from this Acidic Glavenus
light bowgun secrete acid inside
prey, further weakening them.
222:
All life trembles before the
howls produced by this Seething
Bazelgeuse light bowgun.
224:
The Nargacuga parts used in this
light bowgun are sharp enough to
cut you just by looking at them.
227:
This Great Jagras light bowgun
handles so easily it feels like
an extension of one's arm.
230:
This light bowgun contains the
thunderous force of a Tigrex,
waiting to be unleashed.
234:
This light bowgun inherits the burning
spirit of an Azure Rathalos, whose
blue fire is contained within.
236:
The barrel of this Silver Rathalos
bowgun, radiant like a blazing
sun, proves the wielder's victory.
239:
A light bowgun made from Zinogre
parts. Echoing shots mark
the start of the royal hunt.
243:
Each shot of this Stygian Zinogre
bowgun is a majestic roar, with
the strength to fell wyverns.
247:
A bowgun with a Barioth's might.
This vessel of the snow gods uses
icy bullets to summon blizzards.
251:
Contrary to its blazing colors,
this Coral Pukei-Pukei light
bowgun drains its prey of heat.
254:
A light bowgun made of only
the rarest bones. Powerful
enough to pierce steel.
258:
The icy shots of this Velkhana
light bowgun freeze the final
cries of its prey in their throat.
261:
The fallen revel at every shot
from this unerring Blackveil
Vaal Hazak light bowgun.
265:
An untamed Fulgur Anjanath
light bowgun that barely contains
the furious lightning within it.
269:
Made of Beotodus parts tempered
by the extreme cold, this light
bowgun is shockingly tough.
272:
Like searing hot magma, this
Lavasioth light bowgun can even
dissolve and pierce metal.
275:
The bold fur upon this Banbaro
light bowgun issues a challenge
to any brave enough to take it.
280:
Stout and unyielding, this
Barroth light bowgun penetrates
the earth with each shot.
283:
Brachydios's distinct explosive
slime coats this light bowgun,
blasting the foes it shoots.
286:
A Raging Brachydios light bowgun
whose unparalleled blasts wed forge
tech with extensive research.
289:
An Ebony Odogaron light bowgun.
The man-eating demon inside
lusts for a feast of flesh.
292:
A dragon element light bowgun
hewn from bone, crafted by dark
and forbidden means.
295:
The purifying fire of this Shara
Ishvalda light bowgun consumes
the doubt and pain of life.
301:
Darkness comes on the unfurled 
wings of this Namielle light
bowgun, ushering in the end.
307:
A light bowgun made from Savage
Deviljho parts. Its hungry fangs
pursue foes even beyond the grave.
309:
A tri-barreled light bowgun made
from Rajang parts, with firepower
that's completely off the charts.
311:
A light bowgun with three barrels
held together by Furious Rajang rage.
Resounds with peerless thunder.
313:
This Alatreon light bowgun
empowers one with ruinous
intent that cannot be resisted.
319:
Brute Tigrex materials tempered
black make this light bowgun
spectacularly destructive.
321:
Bestowed upon guild knights with
stellar achievements. The sublime
glow is a source of pride.
328:
A silver Frostfang Barioth light
bowgun enveloped by a sharp cold.
Proof of the hoarfrost's keeper.
330:
The wicked wings of this Fatalis
light bowgun fires a devastating
shot to the soul of its user.
344:
A light bowgun made from Safi'jiiva
parts. Awaken its hidden potential
by using unique materials.
